		<hr size="1">Woah! You guys haven't even mentioned the tactical use of begging...... TAUNT for non-tanks.  You will have to turn attack off for a moment, beg from NPC (repeat if necessary), & attack again.  This can give your tank a few minutes to heal up, then they can taunt back.  I would much rather take my hits while the tanks are still up & doing damage, then wait till they die & hope I can stand toe to toe.<BR><br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
